{"tid":1510860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞官員指出：「唔歡迎反修例嘅人士」","createTime":"2019-08-27T10:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T10:48:31.000Z","uid":78947,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4560127907ff0881dae63d30ff88032bc4bc7740","tid":1510860,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"【移民注意】反修例風波持續，唔少香港人萌生出走嘅念頭，台灣、美加等都係港人熱門目標，新興的國家就有馬來西亞等。<br />\n大馬嘅「第二家園計劃」入場門檻較低，最低門檻係申請人只要35萬令吉(約65萬港元)存款，及月入超過1萬令吉(約1.9萬港元)，就可以申請！獲批之後，除咗可以保留自己國藉之餘，仲可以享有稅務優惠！<br />\n不過，馬來西亞官員指出，唔歡迎反修例嘅人士，如果發現申請人曾參與遊行，就唔批准申請！<br />\n#投資移民 #唔係有錢就得 <br />\n#第二家園計劃 #馬來西亞<br />\n#Now財經台 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/now.comFinance/photos/a.575165749175313/3199221190103076/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnow.comFinance%2Fphotos%2Fa.575165749175313%2F3199221190103076%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=4abf2a9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/now.comFinance/photos/a.575165749175313/3199221190103076/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"3237db4b081df62f8198357928143574b7683277","tid":1510860,"uid":269724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"無人想來囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28847006320426d0f1824b2cc1efb4533f461440","tid":1510860,"uid":225818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:40:28.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"37227c02618f70108e006ea880e7fcf1459831fc","tid":1510860,"uid":267647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"口交部：不容許外國勢力對中國內部事務說三道四"},{"pid":"f308ab2ed16588153574da34ac32dede5b5a9a57","tid":1510860,"uid":277920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"哦，我去台灣不好？去馬來西亞做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不了<img src=\"